quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  15,50,"And that My torture, it is the torture, the painful"
  15,51,And inform them about Abraham`s guests
  15,52,"When/if they entered on (to) him, so they said: \"Greeting/peace .\" He said: \"That we are afraid/apprehensive from you"
  15,53,"They said: \"Do not be afraid/apprehensive, that we, we announce good news to you with (of) a knowledgeable boy (new son)"
  15,54,"He said: \"Did you announce good news to me on that the old age touched me so with what (do) you announce177good news to me"
  15,55,"They said: \"We announced to you with the good news, so do not be from the despaired/despairing"
  15,56,"He said: \"And who despairs from his Lord`s mercy, except the misguided"
  15,57,"He said: \"So what (is) your matter/affair/concern, you, the messengers"
  15,58,"They said: \"We are sent to a nation (of) criminals/sinners"
  15,59,"Except Lot`s family, We are saving/rescuing them (E) all together"
  15,60,Except his woman (wife). We predestined/evaluated that she truly is from (E) the remaining behind
  15,61,So when the messengers came (to) Lot`s family
  15,62,"He said: \"That you are a disguised/unknown nation"
  15,63,"They said: \"But we came to you, with what they were in it doubting/arguing"
  15,64,"And we came/brought (to) you with the truth , and that we are truthful (E)"
  15,65,"So move/travel/depart at night with your family/people with portions from the night and follow their backs/ends; and no one from you (should) turn around , and proceed/complete where/when you are being ordered/commanded"
  15,66,"And We ordered/passed judgment to him (of) that the matter/affair/order/command, that those (people`s) root/remainder (is) cut off/severed by the morning/daybreak"
  15,67,And the city`s/town`s people came cheerful/rejoicing
  15,68,"He said: \"That those (are) my guests, so do not expose my faults (scandalize me)"
  15,69,And fear and obey God and do not shame/disgrace me
  15,70,"They said: \"And did we not forbid/prevent you from the creations all together/(universes)"
  15,71,"He said: \"Those (are) my daughters, if you were making/doing"
  15,72,To your life/age (an oath) that they truly are in (E) their intoxication/loss of judgment being confused/puzzled
  15,73,So the loud strong cry/torture raid took/punished them at sunrise
  15,74,"So We made its highest/elevated , its lowest/bottom, and We rained on them stones of dry and hardened mud"
  15,75,"That in that (are) evidences/signs (E) , to the observing/scrutinizing"
  15,76,And that it truly is with a continuing/keeping up path/means (E)
  15,77,That in that (is) a sign/evidence (E) to the believers
  15,78,And if owners/company (of) the thicket/dense tangled trees were unjust/oppressive (E)
  15,79,So We revenged from them that they (B) truly (the two nations) are with a clear/evident leader/example (E)
  15,80,And the forbidden`s/mind`s owners/company denied the messengers
  15,81,"And We gave/brought them Our verses/evidences , so they were objecting/opposing/turning away from it"
  15,82,And they were carving out/cutting from the mountains houses/homes safely/securely
  15,83,So the loud strong cry/torture raid took/punished them in the morning/daybreak
  15,84,So what they were gaining/acquiring did not enrich/suffice them from them (was of no benefit to them)
  15,85,"And We did not create the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth and what (is) between them (B) except with the truth , and that truly the Hour/Resurrection is coming (E) so forgive/pardon the forgiveness/pardon, the beautiful/graceful"
  15,86,"That truly your Lord (is) the creator (E), the knowledgeable"
  15,87,"And We had given/brought you seven from the doubles/strength/capacity and the Koran , the great"
  15,88,"Do not extend/spread your two eyes to what We made spouses/couples from them enjoy with it, and do not be sad/grievous on (for) them, and be lenient/comforting/lower your wing/side (kindness) to the believers"
  15,89,"And say: \"That I, I am the warner/giver of notice, the clear/evident"
  15,90,As We descended on the apportioners/dividers/distributors
  15,91,Those who made the Koran bits/divisions/enchantments
  15,92,"So by/with your Lord, We will ask/question them (E) all together"
  15,93,About what they were making/doing
  15,94,"So uncover/declare openly with what you are being ordered/commanded, and turn away from the sharers/takers of partners (with God)"
  15,95,That We truly make you sufficient (protect you) against the mocking/making fun
  15,96,"Those who create/put with God another god, so they will/shall know"
  15,97,"And We had know (known) that you, your chest (innermost) narrows/tightens becuase (of) what they say"
  15,98,"So praise/glorify with your Lord`s praise/gratitude/thanks, and be from the prostrating"
  15,99,"And worship your Lord, until the assurance/certainty (death) comes to you"